import React from "react"
import PrimarySearchAppBar from "../component/Navbar"
import { Box, Typography } from "@mui/material"
import styled from "styled-components"

const BoxFirst = styled(Box)`
  display: flex;
`


const SectionFirst=styled(Box)`
  position: relative;
  top: 73px;
  
`

export const HomeScreen = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <PrimarySearchAppBar></PrimarySearchAppBar>
      <SectionFirst>
        <BoxFirst>
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h5">Mobile</Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h5">Electronics</Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h5">Fashion</Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h5">Furniture</Typography>
          </Box>
        </BoxFirst>
        </SectionFirst>
    </>
  )
}
